name: Grid #1
description:
Grid #1 is a simple yet colorful work where I try to emphasize the power of complementary colors and lines that when in motion can end up creating new shapes as they interact with the background. Rafael de Souza, 2021. 

Size: 1000x1000p
Color scheme: Complementary (saturated)
Dominant shape: Square
